com.tedros.fxapi.annotation.effect

Annotation Type TFloatMap.TSample


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
@Target(value=ANNOTATION_TYPE)
public static @interface TFloatMap.TSample
     Sets the sample for a specific band at the given (x,y) location.
 
 Parameters:
 x - the x location
 y - the y location
 band - the band to set (must be 0, 1, 2, or 3)
 s - the sample value to set
